description.plain:
In this #1 hit from Sorry for Party Rocking, RedFoo shows displays self-confidence and self-awareness in his impressive physique (or at least, what he thinks is impressive physique).

This is his definition of “sexy”, in his own words:

Sexy is confidence. It’s ‘I don’t care what other people think, but I want them to think that I’m sexy at the same time. It’s a Catch-22. I want to be seen. Sexy is you want attention and you gotta have moves. You gotta have moves, whether it be in the bedroom [or] on the dance floor — just the way you walk, the way you talk.
